data.description: Truly a unique but spacious home in Oak Grove. 3 Bed 2 Bath home with a bonus that could be used for just about anything! Take advantage of the large dining area that's conveniently open to the kitchen and the huge living room. Need additional space for actives? Take it on up to the Bonus area about the two car garage! All appliances convey, outdoor blink security camera convey, PLUS the Seller is open to helping potential buyers with Closing Expenses and Rate Buy Down!
